  "siteContent": {
    "founderName": "Mahal Hudson",
    "founderTitle": "Founder — Leadership Coach & Team Advocate",
    "founderBioParagraphs": [
      "\"I'm a dreamer, optimist, and a visionary. I want to feel alive every day — to be brave and authentic, and to empower one soul at a time.\" That line has anchored Avant-Garde Coach since the beginning, and it still does.",
      "Trained through the Co-Active coaching tradition, Mahal works with individuals and teams navigating turning points — the conversation you're avoiding, the decision you're circling, the version of yourself you're growing into.",
      "She's also the author of Superheroes Unmasked: 10 Powerful Ways to Lead Without Fear, and hosts Get Real with Mahal Hudson, a TV talk show built on unfiltered, unbiased conversations about the issues people are usually too polite to bring up."
    ],
